<note n="0412001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0412001">雜無雜＝離無離【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0412002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0412002">三＝二【宋】</note>
